data.description: Welcome to the perfect family home! As you enter you have a formal dining room that can be used as an office or flex room. The large family room is open to the kitchen with a semi open plan. The kitchen has granite counters, kitchen island with plenty of cabinets and a butlers pantry connecting to the dining/ flex room. The primary bedroom is oversized and downstairs with a large bath dual sinks and a closet. Upstairs you have a large loft living room with 4 additional bedrooms on each corner of the house. There is a full bath upstairs as well. Don't miss the opportunity to own this home! It has space for everyone!
